[player]: I believe the ice will break eventually, and your ships will sail again.
[master_oakenheart]: *Fingers tapping on the wooden table, I gaze out at the darkening waters.* The ice may thaw in time, but there are other challenges we must face now. Are you here to offer aid or perhaps seek a ship of your own? The future is uncertain, and preparation is key.
