[master_oakenheart]: I am preparing the plans for a vessel that could navigate even the iciest of waters. Precise timbers, enchanted with cold-resistance runes, are essential. Also, special alloys and enchanted ropes will ensure her strength against the harsh elements. Would you be willing to journey far to find such rare materials?